evaluations should be communicated to the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">individual</ENAMEX> responsible
for the function and also to <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">at least one</NUMEX> level of management above
that <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">individual</ENAMEX>. Serious matters should be reported to top
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">management</ENAMEX>.
